* Windows

- maximize current window - C-x 1
- split into windows horizontally - C-x 2
- split into windows vertically - C-x 3
- open file in new window and move cursor there too - C-x 4 C-f
- move to next window - C-x o
- make current window taller C-x ^
- make current window wider C-x }
- shring window horizontally C-x {
- make all windows the same size C-x +
- move down in the next window - C-M-v - useful when you're taking notes in one window from a document in another window
- delete current window - C-x 0

* Frames
- create new frame C-x 5 2
- move between frames C-x 5 o
- delete frame C-x 5 0
